{
  "stem": "14251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember that either.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Levent and my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because of this terrible cough, they had to take a chance and put me into another space by adding what I am describing was a wooden floor or a hallway all around that whole square of that building with a courtyard in the middle.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a door at every corner that would open and close.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you went through sections-- wanted to walk, say, the whole perimeter of the apartment building or attic.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, every tenant had attic space aside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But many of them had nothing that they were storing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were already run out of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was a building for Jews other than the post office.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so they had to put me every night into a different storage space to sleep [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because they feared the noise would carry despite the carpets.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, vaguely only.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Vaguely, that it was being alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, I was raised not to question anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just don't question anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why am I being left here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Your business was to keep quiet and do what your parents told you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't have time for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they would.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the danger was, what if I had to get up or go to bathroom or something?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you just don't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned to hold it for decades.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I discovered, if you don't eat or drink much, you don't need to go at all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, the drinking went on probably until about five years ago.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I didn't drink, I didn't need to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The magic bladder.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so that started already then, because when are you-- when are you going to go to the bathroom?",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
